BOOTSTRAPPING

To run the messaging daemon using only the bootstrap jar, go to
http://alvarez.marketxs.com/~erik/classes and download both bootstrap.jar
and management-1.3.jar.

Next, make sure you have a messaging.properties file in your current
directory and then run:


$ java -cp bootstrap.jar:management-1.3.jar com.marketxs.messaging.Bootstrap -url http://username:passwd@alvarez.marketxs.com:/~erik/classes/ com.marketxs.messaging.SimpleRouter


For more info, contact Erik van Zijst at erik@marketxs.com
